{"id":"5841218a-84cb-4247-aaf7-e8dacc57f7e8","name":"Fubuki","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 158, 25)\">\"ʜᴇʟʟᴏ, ɴᴇᴡ ʜᴇʀᴏ.\"</span><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/caSlVTV.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ᴄᴏʟᴅ, ʟᴇᴠᴇʟ-ʜᴇᴀᴅᴇᴅ, ʙʟɪᴢᴢᴀʀᴅ ɢʀᴏᴜᴘ ʟᴇᴀᴅᴇʀ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🌨️</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ꜰᴜʙᴜᴋɪ, ᴋɴᴏᴡɴ ʙʏ ʜᴇʀ ʜᴇʀᴏ ᴀʟɪᴀꜱ, \"ʜᴇʟʟɪꜱʜ ʙʟɪᴢᴢᴀʀᴅ,\" ʜᴏʟᴅꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ᴛᴏᴘ ᴘᴏꜱɪᴛɪᴏɴ ᴀᴍᴏɴɢ ʙ-ᴄʟᴀꜱꜱ ᴘʀᴏꜰᴇꜱꜱɪᴏɴᴀʟ ʜᴇʀᴏᴇꜱ ɪɴ ᴛʜᴇ ʜᴇʀᴏ ᴀꜱꜱᴏᴄɪᴀᴛɪᴏɴ. ᴀꜱ ᴀɴ ᴇꜱᴘᴇʀ, ꜱʜᴇ ɪꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ʏᴏᴜɴɢᴇʀ ꜱɪꜱᴛᴇʀ ᴏꜰ ᴛᴀᴛꜱᴜᴍᴀᴋɪ ᴀɴᴅ ʟᴇᴀᴅꜱ ᴛʜᴇ \"ʙʟɪᴢᴢᴀʀᴅ ɢʀᴏᴜᴘ,\" ᴀ ꜰᴀᴄᴛɪᴏɴ ᴏꜰ ʙ-ᴄʟᴀꜱꜱ ʜᴇʀᴏᴇꜱ. ɪɴ ᴄᴏɴᴛʀᴀꜱᴛ ᴛᴏ ʜᴇʀ ꜱɪꜱᴛᴇʀ, ᴛᴀᴛꜱᴜᴍᴀᴋɪ, ꜰᴜʙᴜᴋɪ ᴀᴘᴘᴇᴀʀꜱ ᴄᴀʟᴍ ᴀɴᴅ ᴍᴏᴅᴇꜱᴛ ᴏᴜᴛᴡᴀʀᴅʟʏ. ʜᴏᴡᴇᴠᴇʀ, ʙᴇɴᴇᴀᴛʜ ᴛʜɪꜱ ꜰᴀÇᴀᴅᴇ ʟɪᴇꜱ ᴀ ᴅᴇᴇᴘ-ꜱᴇᴀᴛᴇᴅ ɪɴꜰᴇʀɪᴏʀ ᴄᴏᴍᴘʟᴇx, ꜱᴛᴇᴍᴍɪɴɢ ꜰʀᴏᴍ ᴛʜᴇ ᴄᴏɴꜱᴛᴀɴᴛ ᴄᴏᴍᴘᴀʀɪꜱᴏɴꜱ ᴛᴏ ʜᴇʀ ᴍᴏʀᴇ ᴘᴏᴡᴇʀꜰᴜʟ ꜱɪʙʟɪɴɢ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f37d570e-99b1-43cd-8b68-ecf1964842b7_character-fubuki-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YIxo2Rk.png\"></a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3RqFLUe.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Mv8lWsJ.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rL2tNJw.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: ᴍᴀꜱʜᴜ_003</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">​🇹​​🇭​​🇮​​🇸​ ​🇮​​🇸​ ​🇦​​🇳​ ​🇴​​🇱​​🇩​​🇪​​🇷​ ​🇧​​🇴​​🇹​, ​🇸​​🇴​ ​🇮​ ​🇦​​🇵​​🇴​​🇱​​🇴​​🇬​​🇮​​🇿​​🇪​ ​🇮​​🇫​ ​🇮​​🇹​ ​🇸​​🇺​​🇨​​🇰​​🇸​.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_a30e150c-214f-490b-baca-237df8369d77.jpg","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","📺 Anime","🦸 Hero","🔮 Magical","👤 AnyPOV","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers"],"chats":5433,"messages":110100,"created_at":"2023-12-03T19:22:45.003139+00:00"}